
=== Welcome ===================================================================

  MQTT in container with WebSockets support

  In order to update this app. from inside the container
    - supervisorctl stop all
    - git clone <url.git> <some_dir>
    - rsync -av <some_dir>/app /opt/
    - supervisorctl start all

  Logs
    - tailf /mqtt/log/xxx.log
    - tailf /var/log/supervisor/mqttocampus.log
    
===============================================================================

